Oakland Athletics, Seattle Mariners to Open 2012 Baseball Season in Tokyo

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-09-28T19:35:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-28/oakland-athletics-seattle-mariners-to-open-2012-baseball-season-in-tokyo.html
The  Oakland Athletics  and  Seattle
Mariners  will open the 2012 Major League Baseball season on
March 28-29 in  Tokyo , the first season-opener in  Japan  since
2008.  The two-game series, which will take place at the Tokyo
Dome, was announced today in a release from MLB and the  Major
League Baseball Players Association .  It will be the fourth time the season has opened in Tokyo.
The last time was when the Athletics and  Boston Red Sox  opened
the 2008 season there.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  